<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1917-12-15T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1917-12-15T00:00:00-05:00" n="395" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d395">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 763.72/8202b</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss>
                                    to the Ambassador in Spain</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_WJE1" type="to"><hi rend="italic">Willard</hi></persName>)</head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                            </opener>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-12-15">
                                        <hi rend="italic">December 15, 1917</hi></date>.</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>783. Inform Foreign Office and request it officially to notify
                                Austro-Hungarian Government that in pursuance of resolution
                                mentioned in Department’s 779, December 11, to you, President on
                                December 11 proclaimed that a state of war exists between the United
                                States and the Imperial and Royal Austro-Hungarian Government.
                                Advise consular officers of proclamation.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <persName corresp="#p_LR1">
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                                    </persName>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>